<p><strong>Best for:</strong> Charge nurses, house supervisors, nursing managers</p>
<p><strong>Columns:</strong> Date | Shift | Census | Staffing grid | Incidents | Escalations | Follow-up needed</p>
<p><strong>Why it's underrated:</strong> Charge nurses often need to document staffing decisions for compliance or grievance purposes. Having a physical log that pre-dates any complaint is valuable protection.</p>
<p><strong>Price:</strong> $11.99 on Amazon KDP</p>
</div>

